Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the guilt of all of it and i think as i told you one day i was walking through the woods and\Nsuddenly the totality of all mankind's suffering throughout all of time i don't know how else to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,describe it it was like i realized that it was like it's like the realizations that come forth\Nas you advance spiritually they have no content to them they're just a massive realization
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and when i was struck by that i thought god was creator of everything including all of that\Nand therefore i became an atheist
